      "text": "Every order had the same note: 'Don’t forget to eat.'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 16.32,
      "endSeconds": 19.36,
      "text": "Mia thought it was her boyfriend being sweet."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 19.36,
      "endSeconds": 21.8,
      "text": "He said, 'What deliveries?'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 21.8,
      "endSeconds": 25.52,
      "text": "The orders were paid for by someone named Mia Chen."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 25.52,
      "endSeconds": 28.68,
      "text": "Her exact name. Her exact apartment."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 28.68,
      "endSeconds": 31.44,
      "text": "But the phone number was different."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 31.44,
      "endSeconds": 33,
      "text": "So Mia called it."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 33,
      "endSeconds": 38.12,
      "text": "Across the room, inside her locked closet, a phone started ringing."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 38.12,
      "endSeconds": 40.44,
      "text": "She froze."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 40.44,
      "endSeconds": 44.96,
      "text": "Then the delivery app pinged again: 'Your driver is arriving.'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 44.96,
      "endSeconds": 48.52,
      "text": "A second later, there was a knock."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 48.52,
      "endSeconds": 70.44,
      "text": "Mia looked through the peephole. No driver. Just a paper bag on the floor."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 70.44,
      "endSeconds": 75.84,
      "text": "Inside was her student ID. The one she had lost three years ago."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 75.84,
      "endSeconds": 79.68,
      "text": "And a note: 'I’ve been taking care of you longer than you think.'"
    }
